title: Robert Browning 200th Anniversary Collection
creator: Robert Browning
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox's Robert Browning 200th Anniversary Collection, Volume 1. For this collection, LibriVox volunteers made their own selections from Robert Browning's poetry and prose to celebrate the 200th anniversary of his birth on 7th May 1812. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
